  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover a secret history in OVER THE ALPS, the singleplayer narrative game made by Stave Studios and adopted by Tributary Games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go undercover, evade the police, discern friend from foe and watch out for an unreasonable amount of goats high in the Swiss Alps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/1f3e8b7959a45c028e6463b14e79bd66.poster.avif?t=1739473498\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/1f3e8b7959a45c028e6463b14e79bd66.webm?t=1739473498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/1f3e8b7959a45c028e6463b14e79bd66.mp4?t=1739473498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring two thrilling stories from the minds of Jon Ingold (<strong>80 DAYS, OVERBOARD!</strong>) and Harry Tuffs (<strong>KING OF THE CASTLE, HOUSE OF MANY DOORS</strong>), which will see you step back in time to WWII Switzerland’s awe-inspiring Alpine countryside inspired by vintage travel posters to complete your mission. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/ca7fe2d93887665a32dda5e7773f785d.poster.avif?t=1739473498\" width=700 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/ca7fe2d93887665a32dda5e7773f785d.webm?t=1739473498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/ca7fe2d93887665a32dda5e7773f785d.mp4?t=1739473498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > From a team with a pedigree of experience (<strong>FAILBETTER GAMES, INKLE STUDIOS</strong>), OVER THE ALPS has hundreds of branching storylines, multiple secrets to discover, and the Test Of Character update that overhauled multiple mechanics in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OVER THE ALPS is <strong>available in 15 languages</strong> including Chinese (Simplified & Traditional), German, Russian, French and Arabic, includes controller support and is available for Steam. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Truly Branching Narrative:</strong> Discover replayable stories that change as you make decisions, with multiple endings and secret stamps to be discovered.  <br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/60e8ba3172c0a9c039b9a436f1271cb8.poster.avif?t=1739473498\" width=700 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/60e8ba3172c0a9c039b9a436f1271cb8.webm?t=1739473498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/60e8ba3172c0a9c039b9a436f1271cb8.mp4?t=1739473498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stunning Vistas to Explore:</strong> Inspired by vintage travel posters, discover sweeping landscapes of beautifully-rendered Swiss scenery.  <br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/712ff8dc77a7e202fe1d33bbde90020f.poster.avif?t=1739473498\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/712ff8dc77a7e202fe1d33bbde90020f.webm?t=1739473498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Race Against the Law:</strong> The police are hot on your heels. Stay on the move to remain one step ahead of the law!<br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/ca2f662ad1f8be50107b231e1c4937b8.poster.avif?t=1739473498\" width=700 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/ca2f662ad1f8be50107b231e1c4937b8.webm?t=1739473498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/ca2f662ad1f8be50107b231e1c4937b8.mp4?t=1739473498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stay Undercover: </strong>Struggle to determine friend from foe as you're plunged into the treacherous world of 20th-century espionage. Meet, befriend, and double-cross a colourful cast of characters. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To join fellow stamp collecting, postcard writing and Nazi walloping spies, join the Tributary Discord (see top right)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/e4a4a581c60c233e6e3db07e4c23b4fc.avif?t=1739473498\" width=614 height=164 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover a secret history in OVER THE ALPS, the singleplayer narrative game made by Stave Studios and adopted by Tributary Games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go undercover, evade the police, discern friend from foe and watch out for an unreasonable amount of goats high in the Swiss Alps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/1f3e8b7959a45c028e6463b14e79bd66.poster.avif?t=1739473498\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/1f3e8b7959a45c028e6463b14e79bd66.webm?t=1739473498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/1f3e8b7959a45c028e6463b14e79bd66.mp4?t=1739473498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring two thrilling stories from the minds of Jon Ingold (<strong>80 DAYS, OVERBOARD!</strong>) and Harry Tuffs (<strong>KING OF THE CASTLE, HOUSE OF MANY DOORS</strong>), which will see you step back in time to WWII Switzerland’s awe-inspiring Alpine countryside inspired by vintage travel posters to complete your mission. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/ca7fe2d93887665a32dda5e7773f785d.poster.avif?t=1739473498\" width=700 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/ca7fe2d93887665a32dda5e7773f785d.webm?t=1739473498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227400/extras/ca7fe2d93887665a32dda5e7773f785d.mp4?t=1739473498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p